name: Spaghetti Carbonara
instructions:
1. Cook spaghetti according to package instructions
2. In a skillet; cook pancetta until crispy
3. In a bowl; whisk eggs and cheese
4. Drain spaghetti and mix with pancetta
5. Add egg and cheese mixture
6. Season with salt and pepper

name: Chicken Alfredo
instructions:
1. Cook fettuccine according to package instructions
2. Season chicken with salt and pepper; cook until no longer pink
3. In a saucepan; melt butter and saute garlic
4. Add cream and cheese; stirring until smooth
5. Serve chicken and sauce over fettuccine

name: Caprese Salad
instructions:
1. Slice tomatoes and mozzarella
2. Arrange them on a plate with basil leaves
3. Drizzle with balsamic vinegar and olive oil
4. Season with salt and pepper

name: Beef Stir-Fry
instructions:
1. Slice beef into thin strips
2. Heat oil in a pan; saute garlic and ginger
3. Add beef; cook until browned
4. Add broccoli and bell pepper; cook until tender
5. Pour soy sauce over the stir-fry
6. Serve over rice

name: Chocolate Cake
instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 350F 
2. In a bowl; mix dry ingredients
3. Add eggs; milk; oil; and vanilla; beat until smooth
4. Stir in boiling water
5. Pour batter into greased pans
6. Bake for 30-35 minutes
7. Let cool and frost as desired

name: Margarita Pizza
instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 475F
2. Roll out pizza dough and place on a baking sheet
3. Spread tomato sauce and mozzarella
4. Season with salt and pepper
5. Bake for 12-15 minutes
6. Top with fresh basil and drizzle with olive oil

name: Chicken Parmesan
instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 375F
2. Season chicken with salt and pepper
3. Dip in egg and coat with breadcrumbs
4. Heat oil in a pan and cook chicken until golden
5. Place in a baking dish; add sauce and cheese
6. Bake until cheese is melted
7. Serve over spaghetti

name: Caesar Salad
instructions:
1. In a bowl; mix Caesar dressing ingredients
2. Toss lettuce with dressing
3. Add croutons and Parmesan
4. Serve with grilled chicken or shrimp if desired

name: Pancakes
instructions:
1. Mix flour; sugar; baking powder; and salt
2. In a separate bowl; whisk eggs; milk; and melted butter
3. Combine wet and dry ingredients
4. Heat a griddle; pour batter; and cook until bubbles appear
5. Flip and cook until golden

name: Spicy Tofu Stir-Fry
instructions:
1. Press tofu to remove excess water and cut into cubes
2. Heat oil in a pan; add tofu; and cook until browned
3. Add vegetables and sauce; cook until heated through
4. Serve over rice

name: Lasagna
instructions:
1. Cook lasagna noodles according to package instructions
2. In a pan; brown ground beef; onions; and garlic
3. Add tomato sauce and simmer
4. In a baking dish; layer noodles; meat sauce; and cheese
5. Bake until bubbly and golden

name: Chickpea Curry
instructions:
1. In a pan; saute onions; garlic; and ginger
2. Add spices and chickpeas; cook for a few minutes
3. Stir in tomatoes and coconut milk. 4. Simmer until the sauce thickens
5. Serve over rice

name: Guacamole
instructions:
1. Mash avocados in a bowl
2. Add chopped onions; tomatoes; and cilantro
3. Squeeze in lime juice and season with salt
4. Mix well and serve with tortilla chips

name: Shrimp Scampi Pasta
instructions:
1. Cook linguine according to package instructions
2. In a skillet saute garlic and shrimp
3. Add wine and lemon juice cook until shrimp turn pink
4. Toss with linguine parsley and seasonings
5. Serve hot

name: BBQ Ribs
instructions:
1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat
2. Rub ribs with the dry rub
3. Grill ribs basting with BBQ sauce until cooked through
4. Serve with extra sauce on the side

name: Spinach and Feta Stuffed Chicken
instructions:
1. Preheat oven to 375F
2. Cut a pocket in each chicken breast
3. Stuff with spinach and feta
4. Rub with olive oil sprinkle with seasonings
5. Bake until chicken is cooked through

name: Vegetable Biryani
instructions:
1. Rinse rice and soak for 30 minutes
2. saute onions; garlic and ginger in ghee
3. Add vegetables;rice; yogurt; and spices
4. Cook until rice is tender
5. Garnish with cilantro

name: Avocado Toast
instructions:
1. Toast bread
2. Mash avocado with lemon juice and seasonings
 3. Spread avocado on toast
4. Top with poached egg if desired

name: Fried Rice
instructions:
1. Heat oil in a pan saute garlic
2. Add chicken peas and carrots
3. Push ingredients to one side; scramble eggs on the other
4. Add rice and soy sauce stir-fry until heated through

name: Tiramisu Dessert
instructions:
1. Whip cream until stiff peaks form
2. In another bowl combine mascarpone; coffee; and liqueur
3. Gently fold whipped cream into mascarpone mixture
4. Layer with ladyfingers and mascarpone mixture
5. Dust with cocoa powder and grated chocolate
6. Refrigerate for a few hours before serving
